Class DigitalClocks.ComputeClockInformation

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.visitor.ASTTraverse
      • pta.DigitalClocks.ComputeClockInformation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ASTVisitor
    Enclosing class:
    DigitalClocks

    class DigitalClocks.ComputeClockInformation
extends ASTTraverse
    Class to extract information about clocks: - list of clocks for each module; - maximum value that each clock is compared against or set to; - g.c.d. of all integers used in clock comparisons or assignments.
